In the event of invalidity or unenforceability of one or several provisions of these ToS, the statutory provisions shall apply.\u003c/li>\u003cli>For the purposes of these ToS, a month is defined as a calendar month beginning on and including the Commencement date and ending on that date which is the earlier of (i) the same date as the Commencement date in the following month or (ii) the last day of the following month. If the Commencement date of your Ruptly Pass with monthly payment is March 31, next payment will be processed on April 30.\u003c/li>\u003cli>For the purposes of these ToS we use Greenwich Mean Time (GMT) and all regular payments, renewals and refills will be processed at 00:00 GMT on the date defined in accordance with clauses 7.1, 10.3 and 22.4 of these ToS.\u003c/li>\u003cli>When you register, you may be asked to provide a password.
